  "text": "Inspired by the previous work [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , we propose a concrete identity-based multi-signature scheme (IBMS CR −1) with three-round interactive communications among the marine sensors and the generation of a single multi-signature as an authenticated tag.",
